dct_description_sm: Inset map: section 13 continued western section of the city (1:71,800. 1" = 6,000'). Oriented with north to the upper left. City districts are numbered. "Finial of the City Hall is in Latitude 42°39'06''.4 and in Longitude 73°45'18''.5" Map shows city and ward boundaries, cemeteries, parks, and railroads.
